Q: Token Setup for @rnmapbox/maps in an Expo Project A: <p>To add a key/value to Info.plist and add android string resources in EAS builds, you must add config to your app.json:</p>
<pre class="lang-json prettyprint-override"><code>{
  &quot;expo&quot;: {
    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;MyApp&quot;,
    &quot;slug&quot;: &quot;my-app&quot;,
    &quot;ios&quot;: {
      &quot;infoPlist&quot;: {
        &quot;MBXAccessToken&quot;: &quot;pk.12345....&quot;
      }
    },
    &quot;android&quot;: {
      &quot;stringResource&quot;: {
        &quot;mapbox_access_token&quot;: &quot;pk.12345....&quot;
      }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre>
